column2: select a.Genre_Name, a.ID from (select distinct Track.GenreId as #, Genre.GenreId as ID, Genre.Name as Genre_Name, Track.MediaTypeId as #, MediaType.MediaTypeId as #, MediaType.Name as # From chinook.Track Inner Join chinook.genre on Track.GenreId = Genre.GenreId Inner Join chinook.MediaType on Track.MediaTypeId = MediaType.MediaTypeId Order By ID) a
